{"tid":1563905,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】話你知點解藍絲既「進化」","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:47:09.000Z","uid":261349,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8235cb24214549395aba2836b807450dd79399","tid":1563905,"uid":261349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:37:11.000Z","msg":"藍絲輿論逐步凌厲，有無諗過點解？<br />\n因為中國人都是欺軟怕惡的，卻不是傻子。威脅到自身安全時，牠會很奇妙地縮在一角，任你如何鼓動也不肯出來，這就叫抗爭成本。所以前排勇武抗爭，唬住藍絲卻綽綽有餘。<br />\n<br />\n你一軟下來，牠們就伺機而動，就來欺侮你了。<span style=\"color: red;\">要贏對家，就要比他們更惡，令他們抗爭成本提高。敢打輿論，我們決不能一笑置之，要以人數湧死牠；敢捉跳閘，我們要喝到牠無地自容。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係時候將政府個套還係佢地身上。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895b10c1bc27925e281f434b05c7463cea9bf521","tid":1563905,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"d4ddbd8d8faf07c5a2941685d905d32ee93eb595","tid":1563905,"uid":11454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"中國人社會<br />\n從來都係<br />\n誰大誰惡誰正確"},{"pid":"ae1b1f1